memberOrga:
The AFCDP has more than 800 members, represented by more than 2500 individuals, approximately 500 of which are CIL or DPO. The nature of these members vary greatly, which is one of the strength of the organisation. Indeed, the AFCDP has member as varied as Non-Governmental Organisations, public authorities and bodies, companies, banks and insurances, lawyers or consulting firms.&#xd;
&#xd;
A list of all these members, as of April 2019, is available at this adress : https://afcdp.net/liste-des-membres/
